-- Blast hits Imperial Oil refinery in Ontario: paper
-- 
-- Thu Dec 14, 2006 7:15am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/12/14/businesspro-refinery-explosion-imperial-idUSN1424194420061214

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - An explosion rocked an Imperial Oil 
Ltd. ( IMO.TO ) refinery in Sarnia, Ontario, overnight, the 
Detroit Free Press reported on its Web site on Thursday, citing 
a report on WDIV Local 4 television. 

  A fire at the refinery after the explosion was contained 
and no injuries were reported, the paper said. Refinery 
officials had accounted for all workers.